OL,3,CMetrolink passenger released gas into
OL,4,Ccarriages in three 'disturbing'
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FA man has admitted releasing gas
OL,8,Fduring 'disturbing' incidents on
OL,9,FMetrolink trams across Greater
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,FGhalib Saeed, 31, let off butane gas
OL,13,Fon three occasions after boarding
OL,14,Ftrams on the Bury line. Passengers
OL,15,Fheard a 'hissing sound' and saw a man
OL,16,Fwearing a 'gas mask'.
OL,18,FSome complained of feeling dizzy, but
OL,19,Fno-one was hurt during the incidents
OL,20,Fon 15, 20 and 22 March this year.
