OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FSaeed pleaded guilty to three counts
OL,8,Fof causing a public nuisance. He
OL,9,Fchanged his plea to guilty at the
OL,10,Feleventh hour, ahead of a scheduled
OL,11,Ftrial at Manchester Crown Court
OL,13,FJudge Elizabeth Nicholls warned him
OL,14,Fthat the starting point for such
OL,15,Foffences was a prison sentence. But
OL,16,Fbefore adjourning the case for a pre-
OL,17,Fsentence report, she added: "All
OL,18,Fsentencing options will remain open."
OL,20,FHe will be sentenced in November.
