OL,7,FButane gas is highly flammable and has
OL,8,Fseveral uses, including for portable
OL,9,Fstoves, as fuel in cigarette lighters
OL,10,For as a propellant in aerosols.
OL,11,FFurther details surrounding the
OL,12,Fbizarre case have not yet been
OL,13,Fdisclosed in open court.
OL,15,FIn March how an investigation was
OL,16,Flaunched after multiple reports of a
OL,17,Fman letting off gas on the Metrolink.
