OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,FSaeed was seen boarding the tram while
OL,8,Fwearing a gas mask covering his mouth,
OL,9,Fbetween the Queens Road and Crumpsall
OL,10,Farea. Passengers reported hearing a
OL,11,F'hissing' sound and a strong smell of
OL,12,Fgas.
OL,14,FA passenger who witnessed Saeed said:
OL,15,F"I was sat on the tram and a guy got
OL,16,Fon at Queen's Road wearing a blue face
OL,17,Fmask with an industrial gas mask over
OL,18,Fthe top of that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
