OL,3,CMetrolink passenger released gas into
OL,4,Ccarriages in three 'disturbing'
OL,5,Cincidents
OL,7,F"There was a hissing noise and people
OL,8,Fstarted looking around. And then we
OL,9,Fsmelt gas, it was really strong. One
OL,10,Fgirl who was near him got up and moved
OL,11,Faway from him. People looked really
OL,12,Fconcerned.
OL,14,F"I had a headache and felt dizzy and a
OL,15,Fbit sick. When the tram got to Abraham
OL,16,FMoss, myself and a few other people
OL,17,Fgot off and I reported it to the
OL,18,Fpolice."
