OL,7,FTransport for Greater Manchester
OL,8,Freleased a statement, which read: "We
OL,9,Fare aware of these incidents on
OL,10,FMetrolink and are assisting Greater
OL,11,FManchester Police with their enquiries
OL,12,Fat this time. The safety of our
OL,13,FPassengers and staff is a core
OL,14,Fpriority - everyone has the right to
OL,15,Ffeel safe and be safe across the Bee
OL,16,FNetwork."
OL,18,FThe following day, Greater Manchester
OL,19,FPolice (GMP) said officers had made an
OL,20,Farrest in connection with the probe.
