OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Paddy
OL,8,FConnell, from GMP's City of Manchester
OL,9,FDivision, said: "We fully appreciate
OL,10,Fthat incidents of this nature can
OL,11,Fcause concern in our communities, but
OL,12,FI want to reassure the public that we
OL,13,Fdo not believe there is any wider
OL,14,Fthreat present.
OL,16,F"We have now secured the arrest of a
OL,17,Fman and are working hard to establish
OL,18,Fthe full circumstances of the events
OL,19,Fthat have been reported over recent
OL,20,Fdays."
