OL,7,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,8,FBurnham also commented on the case. He
OL,9,Fsaid: "It's a very worrying incident
OL,10,Fbut my update is that it has been
OL,11,Fdealt with swiftly and somebody has
OL,12,Fbeen arrested.
OL,14,F"My message back to people will be,
OL,15,Fthis is a reflection of how we are now
OL,16,Fmanaging people safety on the Bee
OL,17,FNetwork. It's being policed in a very
OL,18,Fdifferent way than it used to be and
OL,19,Fincidents that do happen will be dealt
OL,20,Fwith in that way."
