OL,7,FDuring a court appearance in April,
OL,8,Fprosecution counsel Neil Fryman said
OL,9,Fof the gas discharges: "He (Saeed) was
OL,10,Fdoing it to the detriment of others,
OL,11,Fthat's the thrust of the Crown's case.
OL,12,FThe Crown says it's very disturbing
OL,13,Fbehaviour, a lot of people were
OL,14,Faffected on a number of occasions."
OL,16,FSaeed was due to face trial earlier on
OL,17,FTuesday, 23 September, but changed his
OL,18,Fplea to guilty.
